[Student "S"]
{SOUTH makes a Support Cue-bid of 2\D to show his Limit Raise in \Ss.

NORTH thinks slam and bids Blackwood to make sure they aren't off two Aces.

SOUTH says he has one so NORTH bids the slam.}

